                "text": "<p>Treat your guests to a worry-free celebration with DrinkAid's custom sleeves 🥂</p><ul><li>$2.50 per sachet (+S$75 custom fee)</li><li>Individually packed sachets of DrinkAid capsules with custom sleeves</li><li>Free shipping and delivery</li><li>Minimum order of 100 sachets</li></ul><p><br/>You can share your own artwork based on a sleeve template, or work with DrinkAid’s in-house design team to create a unique sleeve for your event (up to 2 revisions)! Please allow ~3 weeks lead time, once your design is finalized.</p><p><br/>Send us your order via the contact form below!</p><ul><li>🎉 5% off for orders of 200 sachets or more.</li><li>🎉 10% off for orders of 300 sachets or more.</li></ul><p><br/>Based on experience, we recommend one sachet per guest - some may consume more than one, while others might not at all.</p>",
